# Country-wise COVID-19 Analysis - Power BI Dashboard

This project visualizes the global COVID-19 situation with a focus on regional and country-wise breakdowns using Power BI.

## 📊 Dashboard Highlights

- Total confirmed, recovered, death, and active cases
- Highest new cases by country
- Weekly increase in cases
- Active cases by region
- Pie chart of cases by WHO region

![Dashboard Screenshot](dashboard.png)

## 🛠️ Tools Used

- Power BI
- COVID-19 dataset (source: [mention source if available])
- Data modeling and DAX measures

## 📁 Files

- `CovidDashboard.pbix`: Power BI file
- `dashboard.png`: Dashboard screenshot

